{"tid":1471873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果港共死都唔跪低咁點？","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:23:35.000Z","uid":4672,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"336611ff7bccf2fabd6c9c90284578d78f4045a3","tid":1471873,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"檯底共產黨繼續冷處理 <br />\n幫牆內賤民洗腦 敵對香港人<br />\n<br />\n檯面港共繼續每日記者會 <br />\n林病繼續做錄音機 繼續用警察做盾<br />\n<br />\n中共成個策略就係咁 <br />\n等你地自然消退 再秋後算賬"},{"pid":"d22561da0c44eea567597fb7943c78565155b883","tid":1471873,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8vxhfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8vxhfe.png&h=9e5f690c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=ecc06d08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"041fb5968da6da05567e8191b6980553a5ea144b","tid":1471873,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要搵佢地弱點"},{"pid":"5e17dca6aab8ced9bbd2368ea07f188c80f47783","tid":1471873,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94a06407d62f96d64fd3c5a4f62b68c017196141","tid":1471873,"uid":274161,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"睇下劉細良個預測： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N6axzmrSIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6N6axzmrSIo&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3Un12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=3f1c9466\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N6axzmrSIo</a><br />\n<br />\nHighlight：<br />\n<br />\n新疆式維穩如何應用於香港：<br />\n警鐘長鳴不放鬆（長期篤灰和監控）<br />\n堅決打好組合拳（多種武力、臥底）<br />\n改善民生聚民心（打經濟牌、派糖）<br />\n快速處置出重拳（主動出擊、快速起訴）<br />\n<br />\n主動出擊的幾大表現：<br />\n1. 拘捕而非驅散 <br />\n2. 拘捕女性，並系鏡頭面前粗暴對待，而達到恐嚇同震懾效果 <br />\n3. 擺臥底收料，甚至煽動衝擊 <br />\n4. 製造恐慌，如在室內放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n預測：不和不戰，長期鬥爭。<br />\n不和：絕對無可能成立獨立調查，因為黑警已經撕破臉，突破底線，無惡不作，翻不到身。<br />\n不戰：不會出解放軍，因為代價太大，攬炒。<br />\n長期鬥爭：政府犯錯太多，無法逆轉民心。市民與黑警之間將長期對立​​。<br />\n<br />\n中共之後的措施：<br />\n1. 大清洗：教育界、公務員、紀律部隊。 <br />\n2. 加速改造經濟結構：經濟屆已經開始吹大雞表態。 <br />\n3. 改造金融中心管理層：近日匯豐兩高管辭職。 <br />\n4. 數碼監控：智能燈柱、新身份證。<br />\n<br />\n點算：公民抗暴、光復香港。"},{"pid":"5b92b74f54f1d2eb9db1d07e03ef8b70c0126ab6","tid":1471873,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"041fb5968da6da05567e8191b6980553a5ea144b","tid":1471873,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要搵佢地弱點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨弱點<br />\n<br />\n紅色貴族利益 <br />\n政權不穩 例如國民起義<br />\n殺身之禍"},{"pid":"d4e95b0554b51052adc75c1c4d80adeccf08f100","tid":1471873,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"求推sorry<br />\n816行動到而家都上唔到熱門？（3）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c0e460a936403f304b257b95d661cabafd5ab94","tid":1471873,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a06407d62f96d64fd3c5a4f62b68c017196141","tid":1471873,"uid":274161,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"睇下劉細良個預測： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N6axzmrSIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6N6axzmrSIo&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3Un12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=3f1c9466\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/